## NEVER DO

Never allow uncontrolled execution of agents.

Never execute workflows without state tracking.

Never ignore runtime failures.

Never bypass observability requirements.

Never mix runtime logic with domain logic.

Never allow non-deterministic execution without control.

Never execute without traceability.

